description:
Plot: A secret agent based in Hong Kong goes after an international crime ring. The story is set in motion when a jeweler is robbed of a million dollars' worth of diamonds. Li chases after the thieves, and by and by catches up with them. 

Overview: Bruce Li plays an undercover detective sent in to unravel a counterfeit operation run by Han Ying Chieh (Fists Of Fury) and Bolo Yeung (Enter The Dragon). Bruce shines as an actor and dazzles his audience with an original display of martial arts talent in this action-packed martial arts adventure.
